                  "revisionId": 2710488,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Compared to a base elemental mod (+90%) in terms of raw damage, Primed Heavy Trauma becomes more effective at rank 9 when a weapon's Impact damage exceeds 60% of total weapon damage. This does not take damage type multipliers into consideration."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
