                  "pageId": 633627,
                  "revisionId": 2710488,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Compared to Primed Pressure Point , they share the same % bonus, but Primed Heavy Trauma uses 12 mod capacity instead of 14, making it more cost efficient only if more than 85.7% of a weapon's base damage is Impact damage."
                }
